scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 357-581 contain the full Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, including the Preamble, Parts 1-5, and all elections, representations, and amendments specific to the parties. The Schedule begins at line 357 ('SCHEDULE to the 2002 Master Agreement') and ends at line 581 ('- Signature page to follow -'). This span excludes the standard pre-printed Master Agreement, CSA annexes, and Confirmations, focusing solely on the negotiated Schedule.
